examples.en: They attributed their success to hard work.
He attributed the change to their marriage.
We attributed this quotation to Shakespeare.
The statement is attributed to Downing Street sources.
Both candidates possess the attributes we want in a leader.
They attributed the quick rescue to the well-trained police force.
The interviewer asked me what I consider to be my best attribute.
Melinda attributed her recent weight gain to the medication she was taking.
Much of his success as a politician can be attributed to his personal magnetism.
The subject of the spirited colloquy was the disputed authorship of the plays attributed to Shakespeare.
